---
// About section with scroll-triggered reveals
---

<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="about__container">
    <div class="about__intro reveal">
      <p class="about__lead">
        The constant across every domain is product instinct.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about__content stagger">
      <p>
        I've shipped across healthcare, logistics, and ML infrastructure—risk
        dashboards, last-mile platforms, annotation tools, design systems.
        Different problems, same approach: prototype fast, validate early,
        iterate toward something that works.
      </p>

      <p>
        Then I proved it end-to-end: launched a Kickstarter-funded TTRPG,
        shipped a mobile game, sold character goods at gaming events. From
        taste to build to audience to revenue—full ownership, zero safety net.
      </p>

      <p>
        I'm most useful on 0-to-1 builds where product direction matters more
        than premature optimization. I design, I code, and I know which
        trade-off to make when.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about__currently reveal">
      <h2 class="about__currently-title">Currently</h2>
      <ul class="about__currently-list">
        <li>
          <span class="about__currently-label">Learning</span>
          <span class="about__currently-value">VR, Unity</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="about__currently-label">Reading</span>
          <span class="about__currently-value">Designing Design</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: var(--space-xl) var(--gutter);
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about__container {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .about__intro {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .about__lead {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.3;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .about__content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .about__content p {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* Currently section */
  .about__currently {
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
    padding-top: var(--space-lg);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-subtle);
  }

  .about__currently-title {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .about__currently-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .about__currently-list li {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    align-items: baseline;
  }

  .about__currently-label {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-muted);
    min-width: 80px;
  }

  .about__currently-value {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .about {
      padding: var(--space-lg) var(--gutter);
    }

    .about__lead {
      font-size: var(--text-xl);
    }
  }
</style>
